		{
			dependencies: ["32E5BB2EC0EE79E6"]
			description: [
				"&aMagpies&r often scrounge up useful items, like &9iron ingots&r. They will happily drop these in exchange for &9seeds&r that are lying around."
				""
				"With some clever usage of &9droppers&r, you can semi-automate this process. Then sit back and let the passive income roll in."
				""
				""
				"(&aKingfishers&r will also occasionally scrounge up useful items, but you will have to pry them from their cold, dead beaks.)"
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
