		{
			dependencies: ["1023B9A16DFDA09C"]
			description: [
				"The &aPlatypus&r is a strange creature. But even strange friends can be helpful."
				""
				"When given &9marine food&r or &9redstone&r, he will get charged up, seek out the nearest &9clay block&r, and dig up useful materials for you."
				""
				"The &aPlatypus&r can be easily transported inside a &9water bucket&r."
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
