		{
			description: [
				"As a zookeeper, you will need to learn a variety of methods for capturing animals. Luckily, most birds are easy to catch! Just construct a &9bird cage&r to catch it in."
				""
				"You can use it as a decoration in your house, or release the bird back into a more convenient location. And they are 100% reusable!"
				""
				"(Note that this will only work on the birds from the Exotic Birds mod, ie: not the noble Chicken, or those from Alex's Mobs.)"
			]
			id: "2C392589E2568FD8"
			optional: true
			rewards: [{
