		{
			description: [
				"If you want to try something differen, consider &aRabbits&r for your &9wool&r source. Fluffy rabbits will produce &61&r &9white wool&r when sheared, and they are the fastest breeder of any of these animals."
				""
				"Here's what else you might want to know:"
				"- &aRabbits&r will give birth to &61-13&r kits at a time."
				"- You'll find fluffier &aRabbits&r in colder biomes."
